*Sredio* je svoj stan za goste. (He tidied up his apartment for the guests.)

*Srediti* će svoje nameštaj. (He will arrange his furniture.)

*Sredili* su svoju kancelariju. (They organized their office.)

*Srediće* svoju sobu. (He will organize his room.)

*Sredila* je svoju sobu. (She tidied up her room.)

*Sredila* bi svoju sobu. (She would tidy up her room.)